{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"4506","heading":"Termination","label":"4506 Termination","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/ch71","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in Text, referred to in subsec. (b), was repealed by .Section 4502(d) of this titlesection 4502(e) of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"determines that all of the restitutionary amounts to which applies have been collected and disbursed as provided in this chapter; andsection 4501(a) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"submits to Congress the final report required by .section 4505 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Such final report shall include the determination (and the justification thereof) described in paragraph (1)(A). Such report shall also be published in the Federal Register.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Exception","label":"b Exception","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s4506","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs4506%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The requirements of section 4502(d) of this title shall continue to be applicable to the use of restitutionary amounts received under this chapter as long as such funds remain available.1See References in Text note below.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
